Mike Tammadge of the Middelburg Mall said the robbery happened on Thursday at about 16:54. Four of the armed men entered the store and made off with cell phones. The men only spent two minutes inside the store. Mr Tammadge said the security personnel noticed the armed men and kept shoppers from entering the scene and no shots were fired. He also added that the registration number of the getaway vehicle, the criminals was used was false. A business robbery case was opened with the Middelburg Police.